ning sets.<\\/p><h2>3. The R-package<\\/h2><p>KeyGenes is made available as an R-package.<\\/p><h3>3.1 Installation<\\/h3><p>You can install the R-package by running the following command in R:<\\/p><p>devtools::install_github(\\u201cDavyCats\\/KeyGenes\\u201d, branch=\\u201dmaster\\u201d)<\\/p><h3>3.2 Usage<\\/h3><p>A vignette explaining the usage of the R-package can be found here: <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/davycats.github.io\\/KeyGenes\\/v0.1.html\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/davycats.github.io\\/KeyGenes\\/v0.1.html<\\/a><\\/p><p><strong>Click Here to show the documentation for the original (and obsolete) R scripts.<\\/strong><\\/p><h2>References:<\\/h2><p>Cnop, M., Abdulkarim, B., Bottu, G., Cunha, D.A., Igoillo-Esteve, M., Masini, M., Turatsinze, J.V., Griebel, T., Villate, O., Santin, I., et al. (2014). RNA sequencing identifies dysregulation of the human pancreatic islet transcriptome by the saturated fatty acid palmitate. Diabetes. 63(6): 1978-1993.<\\/p><p> Fagerberg, L., Hallstrom, B.M., Oksvold, P., Kampf, C., Djureinovic, D., Odeberg, J., Habuka, M., Tahmasebpoor, S., Danielsson, A., Edlund, K., et al. (2014). Analysis of the human tissue-specific expression by genome-wide integration of transcriptomics and antibody-based proteomics. Molecular &amp; cellular proteomics: MCP. 13(2): 397-406.<\\/p><p> Friedman J., Hastie T., and Tibshirani R. (2010). Regularization paths for generalized linear models via coordinate descent. Journal of statistical software. 33(1): 1-22.<\\/p><p> Roost M.S., van Iperen L., Ariyurek Y., Buermans H.P., Arindrarto W., Devalla H.D., Passier R., Mummery C.L., Carlotti F., de Koning E.J.P., van Zwet E.W., Goeman J.J., and Chuva de Sousa Lopes S.M. (2015). KeyGenes, a tool to probe tissue differentiation using a human fetal transcriptional atlas. Stem Cell Reports. 4(6):1112-24.<\\/p>\",\"sort\":null,\"created_by\":\"1\",\"created_on\":\"2019-08-02 10:47:49\",\"modified_by\":\"1\",\"modified_on\":\"2019-08-02 10:47:58\"}','